 <p style="color:Purple; font-size:larger;">1.&nbsp;&nbsp; C O N T E N T</p>
 <p><i>Digi Journal - Mart</i> publishes full articles, brief notices, book-reviews, conference 
 reports, project briefings, opinions, letters, and pointers of broad 
 interest.</p>

 <p>Full articles should be:</p>
 <p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt&gt be of interest to a broad community, and<br />
 &nbsp;&nbsp;&gt&gt reflect work that has been completed, rather than just beginning.
</p>
 <p>Articles should not have been published previously in another magazine or 
 journal, nor been available in a final version on a publicly available 
 website.</p>

